{"tid":24270,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法玩到3ds逆轉裁判中文版？","createTime":"2016-12-05T12:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T10:01:57.000Z","uid":23382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5217195a142885dc5abe9a273123dd54836bcdc","tid":24270,"uid":23382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n我真係好想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲啲應該會學日文<br />\n但我好想依家玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4d06068e15d4d70f0dac3be6beae8e127c41b3","tid":24270,"uid":1135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"逆轉有出過中文版咩"},{"pid":"5441ec83e9c8f22e870f0390a40b2bbbd4973c7a","tid":24270,"uid":22651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逆轉有出過中文版咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n官方中文就冇 不過有漢化組整過<br />\n1234都有漢化<br />\n1可以玩nds果隻復蘇的逆轉<br />\n2同3得GBA有漢化,nds嘅移植版係冇<br />\n5同6就得日文版"},{"pid":"06803f9bd566330c82598feade83b0bfb59326c6","tid":24270,"uid":23382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>逆轉有出過中文版咩</blockquote>官方中文就冇 不過有漢化組整過1234都有漢化1可以玩nds果隻復蘇的逆轉2同3得GBA有漢化,nds嘅移植版係冇5同6就得日文版</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我1-4已經玩曬 係差3ds 個兩隻<br />\n5 6我見上網都有人漢化<br />\n但我唔識破解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：平時買開正版 破解整係想玩呢隻"},{"pid":"8f16496a5211b1269d7d9e4154781a4897c36364","tid":24270,"uid":49445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"5,6 唔好玩， 可以慳返d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a058623c97f6b98873ebf8e71e88f4a5c21b9c","tid":24270,"uid":56410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5,6 唔好玩， 可以慳返d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6唔好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6劇本已經係最接近3個質素，王泥喜終於似番個主角，最後個關長得黎twist又做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5就一般, 好過4咁囉<br />\n<br />\n利申：5, 6玩英文<br />\n<br />\n想玩大逆轉但破解好複雜唔咁搞"},{"pid":"7e86ba46f3ee1cccfe8e3934cb3993cc0f432dae","tid":24270,"uid":49445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5,6 唔好玩， 可以慳返d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6唔好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6劇本已經係最接近3個質素，王泥喜終於似番個主角，最後個關長得黎twist又做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5就一般, 好過4咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：5, 6玩英文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想玩大逆轉但破解好複雜唔咁搞</blockquote><br />\n得最尾個關好少少<br />\n大部份時間禁住個快進玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411b0929c859752e622644a6018b4f19fda473b4","tid":24270,"uid":22651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5,6 唔好玩， 可以慳返d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6唔好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6劇本已經係最接近3個質素，王泥喜終於似番個主角，最後個關長得黎twist又做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5就一般, 好過4咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：5, 6玩英文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想玩大逆轉但破解好複雜唔咁搞</blockquote><br />\n得最尾個關好少少<br />\n大部份時間禁住個快進玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大逆轉買咗番黎未玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想等埋2先玩<br />\n6就爭第五章先玩完<br />\n不過整體劇情係好過5 第三章都幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且可以見番真宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf065e56f7992c52275d85d1bd796b50130ca86","tid":24270,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"3ds破解上多玩睇啦<br />\n不過好似唔係個個version都破到"},{"pid":"d3b052e9fd3d0144231a246864c1f0c6fc33d5c2","tid":24270,"uid":23382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3ds破解上多玩睇啦<br />\n不過好似唔係個個version都破到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實追左好多post <br />\n但部機個version 好似太update <br />\n好似用唔到 所以唔敢試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c463300a84ba47ec290278bf4e23fb0543a96cd3","tid":24270,"uid":56410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5,6 唔好玩， 可以慳返d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6唔好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6劇本已經係最接近3個質素，王泥喜終於似番個主角，最後個關長得黎twist又做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5就一般, 好過4咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：5, 6玩英文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想玩大逆轉但破解好複雜唔咁搞</blockquote><br />\n得最尾個關好少少<br />\n大部份時間禁住個快進玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大逆轉買咗番黎未玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想等埋2先玩<br />\n6就爭第五章先玩完<br />\n不過整體劇情係好過5 第三章都幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且可以見番真宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6最後一關真係好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋第4關同主線無關係打亂左節奏<br />\n如果佢將第4關skip左當bonus stage我會覺得同第三集有得比"},{"pid":"b5d9b36e9ef4de727b751160820f9bbb4cbc8f0f","tid":24270,"uid":22651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5,6 唔好玩， 可以慳返d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6唔好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6劇本已經係最接近3個質素，王泥喜終於似番個主角，最後個關長得黎twist又做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5就一般, 好過4咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：5, 6玩英文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想玩大逆轉但破解好複雜唔咁搞</blockquote><br />\n得最尾個關好少少<br />\n大部份時間禁住個快進玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大逆轉買咗番黎未玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想等埋2先玩<br />\n6就爭第五章先玩完<br />\n不過整體劇情係好過5 第三章都幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且可以見番真宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6最後一關真係好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋第4關同主線無關係打亂左節奏<br />\n如果佢將第4關skip左當bonus stage我會覺得同第三集有得比</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果關根本特登整出黎比心音等佢有d戲份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}